image_analysis.description: A wide-angle indoor photograph of a breakroom or kitchen area. The room features a black and white checkered floor and a drop ceiling with recessed lighting and square fluorescent fixtures. In the foreground, there is a glass-topped table with four grey upholstered chairs. On the table sits a blue spray bottle with a red trigger. In the background, there are several large appliances including a stainless steel commercial refrigerator/freezer and a white residential-style refrigerator. To the right, there is a smaller table with two chairs, a wall-mounted television, and a doorway leading to another room. A trash can and a small step stool are visible near the center.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a single photograph with a text identifier in the bottom right corner.
